{"_path":"/maps/_ai/emerging","_dir":"_ai","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"新兴技术 (Emerging Technologies)","description":"","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h1","props":{"id":"新兴技术-emerging-technologies"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"新兴技术 (Emerging Technologies)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"moe稀疏激活的参数扩展"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"MoE：稀疏激活的参数扩展"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"混合专家模型（MoE）将前馈层替换为多个\"专家\"网络，通过门控网络动态选择激活的专家。DeepSeek-V3 是 MoE 标杆，拥有 671B 总参数但每次只激活 37B，在保持推理成本不变的情况下显著扩展模型容量。2025 年 MoE 成为大模型标配，Mixtral、Qwen3、Gemini 1.5 Pro 均采用此架构。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2412.19437","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"DeepSeek-V3 技术报告"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://cameronrwolfe.substack.com/p/moe-llms","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"MoE LLMs 详解"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"jepa非生成式世界模型"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"JEPA：非生成式世界模型"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"JEPA（Joint Embedding Predictive Architecture）是杨立昆（Yann LeCun）提出的非生成式自监督学习架构。不同于 LLM 在像素/token 空间预测，JEPA 在抽象表示空间进行预测，关注高层语义而非低层细节。2025 年 Meta 发布 V-JEPA 2，结合互联网视频与机器人轨迹数据，在视觉理解上达到 SOTA。VL-JEPA 进一步拓展到视觉-语言多模态领域。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://ai.meta.com/research/vjepa/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"V-JEPA 2 官方发布"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://rohitbandaru.github.io/blog/JEPA-Deep-Dive/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"JEPA 深度解析"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://medium.com/@harshit.sinha0910/what-vl-jepa-could-revolutionize-in-multimodal-intelligence-a1c2105dc62e","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"VL-JEPA 多模态突破"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"空间智能李飞飞的-ai-愿景"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"空间智能：李飞飞的 AI 愿景"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"李飞飞认为当前 LLM 只是\"系统一\"的快速思考，真正的 AI 需要具备\"空间智能\"——理解三维世界的几何、物理和语义关系。世界模型需要具备生成性（创造物理一致的世界）、多模态（融合视觉、语言、空间）、交互性（支持探索和导航）三大特征。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.mittrchina.com/news/detail/15468","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"李飞飞空间智能宣言"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"投机解码推理加速新范式"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"投机解码：推理加速新范式"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"投机解码用小模型（draft）快速生成候选 token，大模型（target）并行验证，理想情况下可加速 2-3 倍。2025 年该技术真正成熟，华为诺亚提出 ViSpec 方法首次实现多模态大模型高效投机推理，加速比达 3.2 倍。与 MoE 结合有协同效应。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://developer.nvidia.cn/blog/an-introduction-to-speculative-decoding-for-reducing-latency-in-ai-inference/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"NVIDIA 投机解码介绍"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://hub.baai.ac.cn/view/49232","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"ViSpec NeurIPS 2025"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"模型合并与长上下文"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"模型合并与长上下文"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"模型合并通过权重空间插值将多个微调模型融合，Task Arithmetic、TIES-Merging、Model Soups 等技术实现零训练集成。长上下文技术包括位置编码外推（RoPE、ALiBi）、Ring Attention 分布式训练，Gemini 1.5 Pro 已实现百万级 Token 上下文。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2212.09849","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Model Merging 论文"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2312.00752","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Long Context Survey"}]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"moe稀疏激活的参数扩展","depth":2,"text":"MoE：稀疏激活的参数扩展"},{"id":"jepa非生成式世界模型","depth":2,"text":"JEPA：非生成式世界模型"},{"id":"空间智能李飞飞的-ai-愿景","depth":2,"text":"空间智能：李飞飞的 AI 愿景"},{"id":"投机解码推理加速新范式","depth":2,"text":"投机解码：推理加速新范式"},{"id":"模型合并与长上下文","depth":2,"text":"模型合并与长上下文"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:6.maps:_ai:emerging.md","_source":"content","_file":"6.maps/_ai/emerging.md","_stem":"6.maps/_ai/emerging","_extension":"md"}